---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About — The Lab">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About The Lab</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">We are an AI-driven innovation lab.</strong>
        Our mission is simple: bring the power of artificial intelligence to local
        actors — businesses, creators, communities, and individuals who are
        building something real.
      </p>

      <p>
        AI isn't just for Big Tech. It's a multiplier. The right tool in the right
        hands can transform a one-person operation into something that punches way
        above its weight. That's what we're here for.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white pt-8">Our Approach</h2>

      <p>
        We don't do hype. We work with real people on real problems. We identify
        where AI creates leverage, build the tools to capture it, and teach the
        skills to sustain it.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 py-8">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Hands-on</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-base">We build alongside you, not from an ivory tower.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Practical</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-base">Every tool we ship solves a real, measurable problem.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Local-first</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-base">We believe in empowering communities, not extracting from them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Open</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-base">We share what we learn. Knowledge compounds when it's free.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">AI Empowerment</h2>

      <p>
        We believe AI should empower — not replace. Our lab is built around the
        idea that when you give people better tools, they build better things.
        We're here to make AI accessible, practical, and powerful for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
